<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Apr1939"><font color="red">15 April 1939</font> <i>NLMS</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Messrs Monro Saw): As you will see from the letter signed by Mr Joyce as from today he has moved to a new apartment, 34 rue des Vignes, Paris 16&deg;, but until it is fixed which will probably take a week or so he is staying at the H&ocirc;tel d&apos;I&eacute;na, Place d&apos;I&eacute;na, Paris XVI&deg;/ </div>
